#### **1. 自定义一个完全支持响应式的 JWT 转换器**

由于 `ReactiveJwtAuthenticationConverterAdapter` 需要一个返回 `Mono<AbstractAuthenticationToken>` 的 `Converter<Jwt, Mono<AbstractAuthenticationToken>>`，我们应当实现一个纯响应式的转化器，而不是直接适配同步的 `JwtAuthenticationConverter`。

实现方式如下：

```java
import org.springframework.core.convert.converter.Converter;
import org.springframework.security.authentication.AbstractAuthenticationToken;
import org.springframework.security.core.GrantedAuthority;
import org.springframework.security.oauth2.jwt.Jwt;
import org.springframework.security.oauth2.server.resource.authentication.BearerTokenAuthentication;
import reactor.core.publisher.Mono;

import java.util.Collection;

/**
 * 自定义响应式 JWT 转换器
 */
public class ReactiveJwtAuthenticationConverter implements Converter<Jwt, Mono<AbstractAuthenticationToken>> {

    private final JwtGrantedAuthoritiesConverter jwtGrantedAuthoritiesConverter = new JwtGrantedAuthoritiesConverter();

    public ReactiveJwtAuthenticationConverter() {
        // 自定义解析 roles 的字段，比如 Keycloak 的 "realm_access.roles"
        jwtGrantedAuthoritiesConverter.setAuthorityPrefix("ROLE_");
        jwtGrantedAuthoritiesConverter.setAuthoritiesClaimName("realm_access.roles");
    }

    @Override
    public Mono<AbstractAuthenticationToken> convert(Jwt jwt) {
        // 1. 提取 JWT 中的权限
        Collection<GrantedAuthority> grantedAuthorities = jwtGrantedAuthoritiesConverter.convert(jwt);

        // 2. 创建 Authentication 对象 (BearerTokenAuthentication)
        AbstractAuthenticationToken authenticationToken = new BearerTokenAuthentication(jwt, jwt.getTokenValue(), grantedAuthorities);

        return Mono.just(authenticationToken);
    }
}
```

##### 替换 `jwtAuthenticationConverter` 的 `Bean` 配置：

```java
@Bean
public Converter<Jwt, Mono<AbstractAuthenticationToken>> jwtAuthenticationConverter() {
    return new ReactiveJwtAuthenticationConverter();
}
```

